OL,5, Parents of a six-year-old with food    
OL,6, allergies have said they faced an      
OL,7, "uphill battle" to get a good selection
OL,8, of school meals for him.               
OL,10,FQuinten from Powys has a severe allergy
OL,11,Fto dairy, egg, soya and nuts.          
OL,13,FHis dad Kam said he "always feels like 
OL,14,Fthe odd one out" with his friends as he
OL,15,Fand wife Ceri try to make progress with
OL,16,FPowys council to avoid him having bland
OL,17,For repetitive meals.                   
OL,19,FThe council said its menus were healthy
OL,20,Fand balanced.                          
